{"lastModified":1765546460327,"uri":"c::9333109022::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Bodrum, Gocek, Fethiye \n\nGulet Smyrna was built in 2003 in the basement. This large and spacious gulet, with a length of 30 m and a width of 6.6 m, provides blue cruise services to our valued guests with its 5 staff. Gulet Smyrna has always been the first choice of those who love blue cruises with its (4 double cabins) spacious air-conditioned cabins. All of our blue cruises on Bodrum or Gocek - Fethiye Marmaris routes with our Smyrna gulet will be a separate pleasure and unforgettable holidays. If you want to explore the Bodrum and Gokova routes with our modern, comfortable gulets that will meet your every need, our recommendation for you is the 4-cabin Gulet Smyrna.\n\nThis gulet has enough sunbathing cushions, seating groups, tables - chairs and service sets for all our guests. This yacht, which offers our Blue Voyage guests a combination of comfort, luxury and peace, reaches 11 nautical miles. While the shower, toilet and air conditioning in all cabins of our gulet will provide you with the comfort you want in your cabin, the lounge section with large seating groups will allow you to have a pleasant time with a bar, stereo speakers for music broadcast, DVD player, backgammon and playing cards.\n\nDeep freezer, refrigerator, ice machine, etc. that you may need during the blue cruise. While you enjoy the meals prepared by our staff in the kitchen equipped with all the necessary technological tools, you can also add different entertainment to your time at sea with surfing, canoeing, snorkeling and fishing gear. Our staff, who will accompany you on the boat throughout your blue voyage, will be with you for meals, daily cleaning, service and whenever you need it during the day. With daily boat rental prices starting from 1.320 euro, Smyrna yacht is ready to host our valued guests who are considering renting a luxury yacht in Bodrum, Marmaris, Gokova and Hisaronu regions. We invite you to accompany us in the comfort of the Smyrna boat in the unique moments of the blue voyage.","blueprint":{"name":"SMYRNA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::17593c50-aa4a-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.png/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b009c970-aa49-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b00842d0-aa49-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b008df10-aa49-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b0092d30-aa49-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b009a260-aa49-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::28a6dcb0-aa4a-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::28a751e0-aa4a-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::28a33330-aa4a-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2cf0e270-aa4a-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2cf1a5c0-aa4a-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2cf30550-aa4a-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f8d-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2cf26910-aa4a-11ee-a071-eb1ded3000f1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/